newsitem.title: USA: Jackson Cty SD, Miss., $4.25 mln won by M. Keegan.
newsitem.headline: Jackson Cty SD, Miss., $4.25 mln won by M. Keegan.

text.p: Morgan Keegan & Co., Inc. said it
won $4.250 million of Jackson Cty SD, Miss., general obligation
bonds, Series 1996 A, with a net interest cost of 5.21 percent.
